description: Performs 20 mc runs at integer undersampling point in the grid [sparsity*signal_nrow, signal_nrow] with james stein denoiser. Sparsity varies from 0.05 to 0.95 in interval of 0.05. No. of rows varies in [100, 150, 200, 250, 300, 350, 400] and no. of columns is 5. Full jacobian computed. cov(resid) used to estimate the noise covariance at each iteration instead of resid.T * resid/n.
